title: Booger
description:
The Booger is a durable mini-twin rocker board built for kids whose focus is park and jibs. It’s ideal for progressing spin, press, and butter tricks and expanding junior's skills on rails, boxes, walls, and kickers.
To learn more about the Booger visit: arborcollective.com/snow/boards/view/436724/booger
